OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,FA Reform UK candidate who stood down
OL,8,Fafter photos of him appearing to
OL,9,Fstrike a Nazi salute appeared online
OL,10,Fhas now been appointed as an advisor
OL,11,Fto the party leader, Dan Thomas.
OL,13,FCorey Edwards was due to be Reform's
OL,14,Flead candidate for Pen-y-bont Bro
OL,15,FMorgannwg constituency in the May 7
OL,16,Felection for the Welsh Parliament, but
OL,17,Flater stood down, citing issues with
OL,18,Fhis mental health.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
