OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779891067
OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,FIn a statement to ITV News at the
OL,8,Ftime, Corey Edwards said the photo had
OL,9,Fbeen "misinterpreted", while
OL,10,Facknowledging he had made "mistakes."
OL,12,FFootage later emerged where Mr Edwards
OL,13,Fappeared to film himself whilst
OL,14,Fdriving and drinking a bottle of beer
OL,16,FWhen asked about Mr Edwards'
OL,17,Fappointment, the MS for Blaenau Gwent
OL,18,FCaerffili Rhymni Llyr Powell said: "I
OL,19,Fdon't like the way other parties are
OL,20,Ftrying to smear Corey here.
OL,26,@zD@Ts|
