OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779891067
OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,F"Other members of that Senedd have
OL,8,Fbeen been banned from speeding, drink
OL,9,Fdriving to a number of areas. I think
OL,10,Fpeople in glass houses shouldn't throw
OL,11,Fstones.
OL,13,F"And I would rather people, than
OL,14,Ffocusing on staff behind the scenes,
OL,15,Ffocus on their criticisms towards me.
OL,16,FI'm big enough, with my shoulders
OL,17,Fopen, so is Dan Thomas.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
