CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1779891067
OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,F"I think leave staff alone. I don't
OL,8,Flike this bullying culture that is
OL,9,Fhere in Cardiff Bay. I'm not prepared
OL,10,Fto stand for it. If the media and
OL,11,Fother critics want to carry on,
OL,12,Ffine..."
OL,14,F"He's got no criminal record, he's got
OL,15,Fnothing that has been held against
OL,16,Fhim. I think it's an unfair challenge.
OL,18,F"Apparently we're living in a nation
OL,19,Fof saints, especially here in Cardiff
OL,20,FBay, where no-one has ever done wrong
OL,21,Fhere."
