OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,FA spokesperson for Plaid Cymru said:
OL,8,F"Rewarding someone who had to resign
OL,9,Fafter making a Nazi salute will raise
OL,10,Feyebrows.
OL,12,F"Once again, Reform have shown their
OL,13,Ftrue colours. It's no wonder the
OL,14,Fpeople of Wales decidedly chose hope
OL,15,Fwith Plaid Cymru over Reform's
OL,16,Fdivision."
