OL,3,CReform candidate photographed
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute becomes
OL,5,Cparty advisor
OL,7,FWhilst Welsh Labour said: "Reform UK
OL,8,Fdidn't have the decency to deem Corey
OL,9,FEdwards unfit to be a candidate. He
OL,10,Fstepped back himself after the truth
OL,11,Fcame out. Now they think he is fit to
OL,12,Fadvise their leader in Wales.
OL,14,F"Reform have shown yet again they
OL,15,Fhaven't learned their lesson and their
OL,16,Fvalues do not align with the people of
OL,17,FWales."
